lead_paragraph: New Zealand pacemen Trent Boult and Grant Elliott shared seven wickets as the hosts bundled out Pakistan for 210 to win the first one-day international at the pacy Basin Reserve by 70 runs on Monday.

headline.print_headline: New Zealand Bowlers Skittle Pakistan After Nicolls Leads Revival
